akr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 16744, "likes": 87, "replies": 4, "retweets": 24, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071186947775549915", "url": "https://x.com/Rigzone/status/2071186947775549915", "text": "The United States Department of Energy announced a conditional loan commitment of $17.5 billion to help 5 nuclear power projects procure long-lead items to deploy Westinghouse's advanced reactor.\n\nhttps://t.co/p7hD6c05gy\n\n#OOTT #energy #USA", "time": "11:00", "author": "Rigzone", "author_name": "Rigzone", "followers": 108893, "views": 1347, "likes": 1, "replies": 1, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071189505650921553", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071189505650921553", "text": "Ukraine struck the Slavyansk-na-Kubani oil refinery in Russia’s Krasnodar region and “reached” a refinery in the Yaroslavl region overnight, President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said on X, calling the attacks part of Kyiv’s “long-range sanctions” campaign against Moscow.\n#oott https://t.co/cYOHPIHi0L", "time": "11:10", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 22253, "likes": 11, "replies": 0, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Russia sanctions", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2071213818068234335", "url": "https://x.com/garquake/status/2071213818068234335", "text": "Marco Macleod Nova Scotia Minister of Energy plan to revitalize oil &amp; gas sector\n\nFrom this clip seems like big Govt nothing burger - Thoughts ?  \n\nNS burned so many bridgers when real Oil and Gas companies tried for yrs to drill  #oott \n\nhttps://t.co/OMKZEQ2sFm", "time": "12:47", "author": "garquake", "author_name": "Burnsco", "followers": 32104, "views": 2810, "likes": 9, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071233269140459847", "url": "https://x.com/DarioCpx/status/2071233269140459847", "text": "JustDarioCigarTime - Episode 83\n\n⚠️ THE LAUNCHPAD IS SET FOR OIL PRICES TO SUDDENLY SKYROCKET 🎙️ \n\n#OOTT\n\nhttps://t.co/psjCixNg2p", "time": "14:04", "author": "DarioCpx", "author_name": "JustDario", "followers": 113107, "views": 133902, "likes": 181, "replies": 22, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 34, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2071261867427889532", "url": "https://x.com/refineryritolia/status/2071261867427889532", "text": "From @Kpler's latest S&amp;D-  Refining margins should remain supported through H2. While crude supply is rising, refinery runs across Russia, the Middle East, and parts of Asia remain constrained, keeping product markets tight and margins healthy. #oott", "time": "15:58", "author": "refineryritolia", "author_name": "Sumit Ritolia", "followers": 402, "views": 926, "likes": 8, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2071279216315006987", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2071279216315006987", "text": "Iran was apparently under a lot of pressure to give the MoU a chance\n\nThis may be an indication they’ve given it that chance.  All can see it didn’t work\n\nIran may be better off applying pressure rather than diplomacy to get what they want #oott", "time": "17:07", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 6979, "likes": 49, "replies": 3, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071281762328567939", "url": "https://x.com/UxbEconomist07/status/2071281762328567939", "text": "If Andy Burnham has any sense he’ll demote Ed Miliband out of the cabinet entirely! \n\n#OOTT \n\n@GMB_union @unitetheunion @The_TUC", "time": "17:17", "author": "UxbEconomist07", "author_name": "UxbEconomist 🇬🇧🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿🇮🇱", "followers": 9438, "views": 904, "likes": 23, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071318321270571249", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2071318321270571249", "text": "This is unbeleivable. each day - new record. \nGiven oil inventories conditioin wti price will feel it soon...\n#oott #Iran https://t.co/Iv5u4uFJMK", "time": "19:42", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 9555, "likes": 121, "replies": 9, "retweets": 13, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071329940461543677", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2071329940461543677", "text": "Peace in the Middle East breaks out just ahead of futures open. #OOTT https://t.co/lgF3gpsmSC", "time": "20:28", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 5329, "likes": 56, "replies": 6, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071347018866295155", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2071347018866295155", "text": "Cynically, there was a 90% chance this was going to happen. US playing Weekend War with the action happening when major markets closed. Iran seems to be playing along (didn’t bomb neighbors, only US facilities) Watch tanker traffic and inventory. #EFT #OOTT", "time": "21:36", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 22330, "likes": 86, "replies": 7, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071363343135408218", "url": "https://x.com/a4_alpha/status/2071363343135408218", "text": "Smart. Fits within the thesis that this sector has nothing to do with war/conflict. \n\nThank you #OOTT #EFT #COM", "time": "22:41", "author": "a4_alpha", "author_name": "A4Alpha", "followers": 7996, "views": 5776, "likes": 33, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071368796711923991", "url": "https://x.com/TheWuhanClan/status/2071368796711923991", "text": "Diesel still &gt;$5 a gallon on average.  Not enough diesel to go around globally and not easily manipulated like fake paper oil market. Goods and transportation prices still surging from high diesel with no relief in sight….   #oott $xle $uso $es $tlt $spx $wmt $amzn $fdx", "time": "23:02", "author": "TheWuhanClan", "author_name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "views": 1943, "likes": 44, "replies": 2, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Refining/products", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071375167394328925", "url": "https://x.com/reasonus4/status/2071375167394328925", "text": "@KobeissiLetter Of course right fake news before futures open. #Oil  should be at $130 right now\n\nBooks will be written o